drm/panel: simple: Add support for Shelly SCA07010-BFN-LNN

The Shelly SCA07010-BFN-LNN is a 7.0" WVGA TFT LCD panel.
This panel with backlight is found in PDA 7" LCD screen (TM70xx series for
instance).

